{
  "id": "RAW_b42974bf",
  "title": "AI 圈最准的消息，都藏在这个小小的 Web3 网站里。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647677803&idx=1&sn=1b804f61d025efa16c324682e47ee2a6",
  "date": "2025-12-15 01:18:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GPT-5.2也发布了有几天了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在发布之后，大家又吵的满头开花，不过实测完之后，确实有一点失望。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过，这篇文章不是来撩GPT-5.2的实测的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而是聊GPT-5.2发布之前的一个很有意思的神奇的事情，就是，在模型发布之前，总能有人，提前预测市场。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很多关注AI资讯的朋友可能都知道，GPT-5.2这玩意，从9号就开始各种小道消息，然后又传13号凌晨2点发。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194076\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2135593220338983\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"590\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40a223b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpt00laood3o4toybvmby6zyoskk87A7kZicN9hd8EHYs4KHkLAeJcV2ibVBRJVwxZFjYpGgQR3ogPw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后又有一群人说不发。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">结果，在一片吵闹中，最后，OpenAI还是凌晨2点把这玩意掏出来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过，一点也不意外。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为我当时几乎百分百肯定GPT-5.2肯定会发出来的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为在各种各样的消息里，有一个平台却显得贼冷静，就跟预言机一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是我11号夜里截的图，里面的每根线，都代表着概率曲线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">橙色的最上面的线，就是预测OpenAI会在12月11号（美国时间）发布新模型，浅蓝色的线是预测会在12号发，天蓝色是预测13号发，黄色则是15号发。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194146\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=62fc86cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKQs9sJjKJMgaMNIuGibPlHxlW2BckHYD7blmiaNDGxIpica3Z6dw02WOVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可以看到，在11号前几天，预测GPT-5.2会在11号（美国时间）发布的概率就居高不下，一直维持在80%以上，除了当天凌晨11点到12点的区间中，有一波巨大的震幅，发布的概率一下子变低了，其他时间的概率一直都维持在非常高的位置，1点的时候，几乎就是100%发了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后的故事大家都知道了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-w=\"592\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6790540540540541\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e26c1a2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpt00laood3o4toybvmby6zHLoLCFmfrYFa9YTrs7pYtxTInmMDhfM9EEtPJS0nvvyspJ07wuTb7g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且不止是11号，早在12月8号，大家都觉得9号会发新模型的时候，这个平台，就一波直线跳水预测，说，明天OpenAI发东西的概率只有百分之五，几乎不可能，大家别等了，洗洗睡吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194136\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9458544839255499\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"591\" data-width=\"591\" data-height=\"559\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=15156e04&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKUG36kCCeTPSWSYaHTdicovj2zEy1q1PXtsgVAOg48WGXFl9jNan6aJw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第二天结果出来，OpenAI确实啥也没发。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个平台说对了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini 3.0 pro，OpenAI浏览器发布，这个平台，都比官方更早给出了信号。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini 3是11月18号发布的，但早在好几天前，预测11月18号发布的概率就居高不下了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194137\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.46075433231396534\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"981\" data-width=\"981\" data-height=\"452\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8139c5b9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKzHFic7tDiacwRO4Xb9PhPic88O0xBjiavcZWDiaBS6wiaOKocE9Eha8jvSDg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后，预言对了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">甚至不止是AI行业模型发布日期的预言。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个平台，还预言正确了奥斯卡最佳影片。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194139\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.44659206510681587\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"983\" data-width=\"983\" data-height=\"439\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dba94dff&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKLGYXQTYdmHmEiaJGkOVywLH2R0IT2clPictNlMmPBgDSDd9LKeRMJibtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">去年预言了漂亮国总统。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194140\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4288681204569055\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"963\" data-width=\"963\" data-height=\"413\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c0cfb35&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MK4AECpJ08LrJs0VCSc7c0GTxv2l66bR3VaBTNb1OofLobr34Qd6j4LQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们自己的官网上，给出的数据也很强：四小时内的预测准确率95%，一天内的准确率88%，一个月内91%。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194141\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1386\" data-height=\"797\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=810c1244&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKmDYseicHT4AqSPh8tbX5COric7CrHwCh1DpNHwD0vFFkd8NGT3WEMFFQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个平台，就是大名鼎鼎的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Polymarket。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也是我现在重要的信息来源渠道之一，说真的，看这个平台的预测，规划我的内容发布时间，提前蹲守，这成功率和准确性，可比看X上那些老外KOL高多了，说实话，很多老外KOL为了流量，那真的是毫无道德底线，什么诡异的谣言和大货都能给你编出来。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给大家介绍一下这个平台。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Polymarket，其实是一个web3交易平台，而你能在这个平台上做的事情，就是预测这个世界即将发生什么，然后下注。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">预测啥都行，从时代杂志2025年度人物是谁，到马斯克一周内发了多少条推特，再到2026世界杯冠军花落谁家。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194142\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6675925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1454\" data-height=\"971\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=09b483f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKn2xlibjuhAKia2CU5f2eO8Ycy1uV3Sibqom1GMnJS3gSdppqTuSQSkSbw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的，啥都行。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你甚至可以看到，预测川普12月会说圣诞老人还是会爆粗口。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194143\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5953703703703703\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1628\" data-height=\"970\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d4391dfa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKvym6kt1F16eZEQUDAHibBYgYaRcVMfQM6Jgiahjx8icOGuXrTSn2PpUtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下注方式也非常简单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你可以把polymarket当成这样一个系统：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这上面的每一个问题相当于一个智能合约，每一个合约都有时限和相应的规则。比如一个问题是，2025年内OpenAI会不会发布浏览器，2025年就是时限，写在下面的这个就是规则。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194144\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2961847389558233\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"996\" data-width=\"996\" data-height=\"295\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=41b06d7e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKiaUbnpWn9iaV7PS92TNEJbIronkPxrSGckEBfOBHgx83icCodoHMRZ7zw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在这个问题也就是合约里，你可以选择购买yes或no。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">yes代表你认为这件事在这个时限内会发生，no则相反。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">每一个yes或者no的价格在0到1美元之间，用稳定币USDC来表示。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个价格和概率挂钩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">代表着市场上所有人认为这件事发生的概率。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果70%的人都觉这个事儿会发生，那么yes币的价格就是70美分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">与此同时，30%的人觉得这件事不会发生，no币的价格就是30美分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">概率是随着两边站队人数增减而随时变动的，币的价格也就会跟着变。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">但是，</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">这两种币的价格加起来，永远等于1美元。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在时限之前，你可以随时买入yes或者no，也可以随时把自己手里的yes或者no卖给别人，没有任何涨跌停、交易时段的限制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">时限到了之后，官方会去查证这件事到底有没有发生，然后给出结果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果对这一步有异议，可以通过质押保证金的方式发起质疑，质疑成功的话，结果会被推翻重新判定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后，结果拍板确定，yes或no的其中一方获胜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所有赢家的代币，按照一票一美元来兑付，输家的代币价值全部归零。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">举个例子，你相信12月11号OpenAI会发新东西，与此同时76%的参与者也相信这天会发。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那么，你下一注的价格，就是76美分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果概率变成80%，你下注的价格就会变成80美分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">等一切尘埃落定，12月11号OpenAI确实发东西了，那你就能赚到1美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">减去你的成本，你就赚了24美分，或者20美分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">反之，如果那天没发东西，你选错了，那你就会损失你之前的投入。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而选了no的人，就可以花24美分或者20美分赚到1美元，净赚76美分或者80美分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194145\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3972222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1348\" data-height=\"536\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1ebca326&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MK8Fqr8gaNcM2LUdA2p5icAvN5OYbcGV1fxNJcE4926ichGFuAEOLfbFfg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">基于这个规则，就产生了两种玩法，一种是押结果，买入一方然后等待现实裁决，要么赚钱要么全赔，纯粹的赌博极致的享受。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">另一种是赚差价，和炒股差不多，吃价格波动，低买高卖。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这就是Polymarket的全部玩法，其实并不复杂。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那问题就来了，为啥</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Polymarket的预测成功率这么高，比那些所谓的掌握着小道消息的内幕人士，靠谱的多？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实原因特别简单，这就是统计学上，一个如磐石般古老的理念。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">叫做，群体的智慧。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在一百多年前，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1907年3月7号出版的《</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Nature</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">》上，有一篇特著名的文章，叫《民众之声》。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">作者是一个英国科学家，叫弗朗西斯·高尔顿。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194147\" alt=\"弗朗西斯·高尔顿- 维基百科，自由的百科全书\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1015625\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 637px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKkPZKibJJbYEMiaZm76uVic6syzwicfu8aqzZffPkITX43MvdiaYFfNb7u3A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1280\" data-cropy1=\"124.01384083044984\" data-cropy2=\"1534.6712802768168\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=68364d76&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKgOzhYXHvqaco46PN0xc3MaJFdhWHicwS8eZoDbxAaQcanYWXd3csOHg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">哦对了，这哥们还有一个身份，就是达尔文的表弟，对，就是提出进化论的那个达尔文。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">高尔顿他在一个乡镇集市上搞了个实验。他让800个人（有农民、有商人，有专家也有外行，总共回收了787个数据）去猜一头牛，被屠宰加工后的体重是多少。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">结果呢，这个实验，把所有人的猜测结果取一个平均值后，得出的最终数字，是1197磅。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而那头牛被屠宰以后，真实的体重是。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1198磅。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比绝大多数单一的专家猜得都准。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这就是群体的智慧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在合适的机制下，一个多元化群体的集体判断，往往比群体中最聪明的那个个体的判断还要精准。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Polymarket，就是就是把猜牛体重这个游戏，搬到了线上，并且加入了一个至关重要的催化剂，那就是，钱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">毕竟，网上投票、搞民意调查不也一样是收集群体智慧吗，但是我们看到的很多所谓的投票和调查，一丁点都不准呢。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为，区别就在于，普通的投票，你发表意见是没有成本的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你可以在网上随便说“我支持A。”，也可以明天就改口“我支持B！”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">这里面充满了情绪、噪音、为了站队而站队的无效信息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但在Polymarket上，你说的每一句话，都得用真金白银来背书。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这就形成了一个极其强大的筛选器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">直接把那些只是想凑热闹喊口号的人给剔除掉了，毕竟，这帮人，不会愿意花钱去下一个自己也不确定的赌注的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而那些那些真正掌握了信息的人，哪怕只是蛛丝马迹，他们有强烈的经济动因去参与。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如，一个在英伟达供应链工作的人，发现最近给OpenAI发货的芯片数量暴增，他可能会觉得看来是要有大动作了，于是他悄悄去买了会发布股。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个在OpenAI工作的员工，听到内部会议说明天没发布计划，他可能会去买不会发布股。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个资深记者，从他的线人那里得到了消息，也会用下注的方式，把他获得的信息注入到市场里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的会有很多这样的人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如有一个哥们叫pony-pony，这个人在12月9号OpenAI会发新模型这个盘上，先是用几乎一整晚上，在90%的价格重仓买Yes，相信12月9号一定会发新模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后在临近时间点时，突然大幅翻仓到no，把自己的仓位从押一定会发，硬拧成了押一定不会发。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194149\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47962962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2795\" data-height=\"1341\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=27dbe410&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKuD4kId7muB9t7Ukk9PgeOcm8I7YCM4j05HZDsZnjZnicTjDnsselWRg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">结果大家都懂的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就因为发布时间这事，这哥们直接赚飞了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194150\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.46060606060606063\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"495\" data-width=\"495\" data-height=\"228\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ce1b20bb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MKx1Wdh086IAQzJN59zXRTQ5GtgUyrgcicJEWWkmI5BJMyicr2huKcLFLQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有一个月前，Gemini 3发布那次，一个刚注册没多久的新账号，一口气掏出了七万八美元砸在yes里，就赌Gemini 3会在11月发布。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194151\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8116710875331565\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"754\" data-width=\"754\" data-height=\"612\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c1aa39c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURouWKrKr01Ew4jvLdbNib9MK9VsGxV7lnUyiavsWS6UmjZjibKcqdFSKC0qdKhJicA0TMFyQkp0wBUpuQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">抛弃掉赌徒心理，虽然我永远不会去下注去赌，但是我还是想说，这些信息，确实是一个还不错的信息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所有这些分散在世界各个角落的、或明或暗的、专业的、业余的信息，最终都通过买和卖这两个简单的动作，汇聚成了那个唯一的不断跳动的价格。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个价格，就成了当下这个时间点，把新闻、数据、专家判断和分散信息压缩成一个更接近现实的概率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这也就是为什么我说，它比看任何一个KOL的分析都靠谱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为KOL可能会为了流量而夸大其词，可能会因为认知偏见而判断失误</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但Polymarket上的价格，是成千上万个用钱投票的人，互相博弈、互相纠错之后形成的动态平衡。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，写到这里，Polymarket的预测到底怎么样，其实我相信，大家心里已经有数了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是我还是想说，我介绍这个平台，是想给大家分享一个我认为更精准、更有趣的信息源，绝对不是怂恿大家去炒币或者赌博。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我想分享的，是Polymarket作为一个现象，它背后真正迷人的地方。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们正处在一个信息爆炸，但智慧稀缺的时代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">打开社交媒体，每个人都在表达观点，每个人都在输出情绪。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一条传言，可以因为符合大众的期待而被疯狂转发，一个KOL，可以因为人设讨喜而获得百万信任。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们每天都在被海量的信息喂养，却越来越难分辨，哪些是事实的倒影，哪些是情绪的泡沫。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">噪音太多了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">所以，有时候，在信息的判断上，不如就用最简单最粗暴的逻辑。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Talk is cheap, show me the money。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，我把它当作信息源，看的，就是那个不断跳动的价格本身。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那个价格，就是当下我们这个星球上，关于某一未来事件最诚实的集体猜测。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">它也会，影响我自己的一些决策方式。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">我自己很喜欢做投资，经常在股市里也会下重注，而现在，在看待新闻和传言时，我可能心里多问一句：“如果让你下注，你敢下多少？”</span></span></ms-cmark-node></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">当你开始这样思考时，你会发现，自己对信息的判断会变得更审慎，更理性。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这，可能就是Polymarket这类预测市场。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">带给我们的最大价值。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克、冯淼</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">wzglyay@virxact.com</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Polymarket 作为一个 Web3 预测市场，通过“群体智慧”与“真金白银”机制，变革了 AI 资讯获取方式，提供超高准确度的未来事件预测。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Polymarket 作为一个 Web3 预测市场，通过“群体智慧”与“真金白银”机制，变革了 AI 资讯获取方式，提供超高准确度的未来事件预测。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了 Web3 预测市场 Polymarket 如何成为 AI 圈内最准确的消息来源之一。作者通过 OpenAI 新模型发布、Gemini 3 发布时间等多个案例，展示了 Polymarket 在关键事件预测上的高准确率。文章深入解释了 Polymarket 的运作机制，即用户对未来事件进行下注，价格反映了市场对事件发生概率的共识。作者将这种机制归因于“群体智慧”理论，并强调了“真金白银”的参与机制过滤掉了噪音和情绪化判断。Polymarket 不仅预测了科技新闻，还准确预言了奥斯卡奖项和政治选举结果。作者提出，Polymarket 的价值在于提供了一个更审慎、理性的信息判断视角，帮助读者在信息爆炸时代分辨真实信息，而非鼓励赌博或炒币。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
